# =============================================================================
# SYNTHFLIGHT PROJECT — LOCAL GOOSE HINTS
# =============================================================================
# Project-specific context for the SynthFlight workspace.
# This supplements the global ~/.config/goose/.goosehints file.
# =============================================================================

## PROJECT IDENTITY
- **Product:** SynthFlight — UAV Mission Simulation and Verification Platform
- **Repository:** github.com/vautieri/one-evening-pipeline
- **DAL:** A (Catastrophic) — DO-178C
- **Coding Standard:** C++17 (ISO/IEC 14882:2017), GCC — see docs/standards/SCS-SynthFlight.md
- **SRS:** docs/requirements/SRS-SynthFlight.md (119 unified requirements)

## WBS STRUCTURE
The Work Breakdown Structure is defined in docs/requirements/SRS-SynthFlight.md.
Always look up the WBS element for the module under test before starting work.

## DOCUMENT MAP
When starting any task, load the relevant documents from this map:
```
docs/
├── cdrl/
│   └── CDRL-Register.md            ← Master deliverables tracker (CDRL-SF-2026-001)
├── plans/
│   ├── PSAC-SynthFlight.md         ← Certification plan (PSAC-SF-2026-001)
│   ├── SDP-SynthFlight.md          ← Development plan (SDP-SF-2026-001)
│   ├── SVP-SynthFlight.md          ← Verification plan (SVP-SF-2026-001)
│   ├── SCMP-SynthFlight.md         ← Config management plan (SCMP-SF-2026-001)
│   └── SQAP-SynthFlight.md         ← Quality assurance plan (SQAP-SF-2026-001)
├── requirements/
│   ├── SRS-SynthFlight.md          ← Unified requirements (SRS-SF-2026-001)
│   ├── requirement-crossref.md     ← Deduplication cross-reference
│   └── raw/                        ← 5 industry-specific raw requirement files
├── standards/
│   ├── SRS-Standard-SynthFlight.md ← How to write requirements (SRS-STD-SF-2026-001)
│   ├── SDS-SynthFlight.md          ← Design standards (SDS-SF-2026-001)
│   └── SCS-SynthFlight.md          ← Code standards (SCS-SF-2026-001)
├── tars/
│   ├── TAR-SF-001.md               ← Math library DAL A verification
│   ├── TAR-SF-001-MCDC-Analysis.md ← MC/DC analysis for math library
│   ├── TAR-SF-002.md               ← Atmosphere model DAL A verification
│   ├── TAR-SF-002-MCDC-Analysis.md ← MC/DC analysis for atmosphere model
│   ├── TAR-SF-003.md               ← Terrain engine DAL A verification
│   ├── TAR-SF-003-MCDC-Analysis.md ← MC/DC analysis for terrain engine
│   ├── TAR-SF-004.md               ← JSBSim submodule integration
│   ├── TAR-SF-005.md               ← JSBSim 6-DOF API wrapper DAL A verification
│   └── TAR-SF-005-MCDC-Analysis.md ← MC/DC analysis for JSBSim interface
└── verification/
    └── SVR-SynthFlight-Increment1.md ← SVR for math + atmosphere (Increment 1)
```

## SOURCE CODE MAP
```
src/
├── math/
│   ├── FGColumnVector3.h/.cpp      ← 3D column vector (1-based indexing)
│   └── FGMatrix33.h/.cpp           ← 3x3 matrix (determinant, inverse, Euler extraction)
├── models/
│   ├── FGAtmosphereBase.h          ← ISA base class (constants, unit conversions, Sutherland's law)
│   └── FGStandardAtmosphere1976.h/.cpp ← 1976 US Standard Atmosphere (9-layer model)
├── terrain/
│   ├── TerrainGrid.h/.cpp          ← Grid coordinate system, elevation data
│   └── TerrainCollisionDetector.h/.cpp ← CFIT detection, alert levels, prediction
└── simulation/
    └── JSBSimInterface.h/.cpp      ← JSBSim 6-DOF wrapper (REQ-SF-0200)
```

